data.description: Modern and Elegant, practically new home in Malloy Terrace Development. Built only 3 years ago, this 4 bedroom (1 bedroom on main level), 2.5 bath house shows like a model home. Top of the line features and fixtures include 19 ft ceilings in the living room, floor-to-ceiling rock wall fireplace, waterfall quartz counters in kitchen with under cabinet and floor lighting, double fridge, large deck off the primary suite, and wrap around covered porch. RING security system and Full Reverse Osmosis water filtration system. This corner lot is the largest in the development and fully fenced backyard.
